org.whispercomm.c2dm4j
Interface Response

All Known Subinterfaces:
SuccessResponse, UnavailableResponse
public interface Response

Encapsulates a response from the C2DM service. This interface includes methods for accessing information common to all responses: type, message, and, if included, updated authorization token.

Some response types include additional information. These are encapsulated by subclasses: SuccessResponse and UnavailableResponse. The specific (sub)class associated with any ResponseType can be retrieved via ResponseType.associatedClass().

Author:
David R. Bild
See Also:
ResponseType, SuccessResponse, UnavailableResponse
